Q. difference b/w Insert and database.insert.
A. whenever we are inserting bulk data if any error occurs then with insert all data will fail but if we use database.insert(subject, false) only failed record will get failed remaining record saves successfully.
Q. what is use of Trigger.isExecuting.
A. Returns true if the current context for the Apex code is a trigger. In triggers also we call class methods, if the method is invoke from trigger then Trigger.isexecuting will be true and if the is not called from trigger than it will return false. 
Q. what is static variable.
A. If you define variable as static, memory will be allocated only once i.e at the time ofloading the class. Static variables referred using class name. once value assigned it will not change it have same value entire process. 
