Q. what is the Recursive Trigger and how to avoid?
A. Suppose in trigger we are calling the one method and in that method we are performing Insert DML operation. Due to this Insert operation Trigger will fire again and execute method again. So it will looping to create records we need to avoid such looping by using Boolean variables.

